        "RESTS",
        "READING"
      ],
      "subtext": "What are Notes and Rests?",
      "voice": "Notes are the symbols we use to read music. Rests are the signs that tell us to be quiet for a moment.",
      "accent": "#ec4899",
      "duration": 25
    },
    {
